ice chair dr muller brings to the company his leadership and organizational skills which assist the board in understanding governance and human capital management issues and in chairing the boards governance and nominating responsibilities his thirty year board membership provides excellent historic reference and perspective insight on company dynamics and knowledge of senior management all of which are of significant value to the board and the company source standex international corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view h n muller iii phds full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like h n muller iii phd more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in h n muller iii phds network and community follow changes in h n muller iii phds employment and moneyinmotion connect with h n muller iii phd through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example h n muller iii phd h n muller iii phds connections  sign up now to view h n muller iii phds  connections » roger l fix chairman of the board and former president and chief executive officer standex international corporation christian storch vice president and chief financial officer altra industrial motion corp thomas j hansen board member mueller water products inc michael a pattison former vice president human resources standex international corporation paul c burns vice pres corp development standex international corporation deborah a rosen former vice president chief legal officer and secretary standex international corporation john bolten former board member standex international corporation daniel b hogan board member standex international corporation thomas e chorman board member standex international corporation gerald h fickenscher board member standex international corporation popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch execut